label: uncl7433
comment: Code specifying the type of agreement.

values.label: User group agreed
values.comment: The description for the type of agreement is agreed within the user group.

values.label: Bilateral agreement between countries
values.comment: The agreement is bilaterally defined by countries.

values.label: Unknown agreement
values.comment: The type of agreement is not known.

values.label: European Union agreement
values.comment: The agreement is multilaterally defined by the countries of the European Union.

values.label: National agreement
values.comment: The agreement is defined at the national level.
